    }

    #[test]
    fn test_burning_on_redeem() {
        // Set up a scenario where stablecoins are burned correctly upon redeeming collateral

        assert_eq!(process_instruction(&program_id, &accounts, &instruction_data), Ok(()));
    }
}
```

Ensure the contract is thoroughly tested under different conditions and scenarios, considering edge cases and stress conditions. Additionally, considering having a third-party security audit conducted to validate your implementation's security and robustness.

### Conclusion

This blueprint outlines the fundamental steps to create a stablecoin standard on Solana. Finalize with comprehensive documentation of the architecture, decision-making process, risk assessments, and code repository to complete the bounty task submission.
